{"tid":1111833,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那人又當自己無講過］華為承認沒有與 Apple 商討銷售 5G Modem","createTime":"2019-04-17T05:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T03:16:47.000Z","uid":55951,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"281fd653c037fc42bb18e100dd2be3f7bc99f3f6","tid":1111833,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"跟 Qualcomm 的官司才剛剛開始，加上 Samsung 不願意供應 5G Modem 晶片，加上 Intel 的 5G Modem 研發遇到阻力，市場對 Apple 如何在 5G 開始起飛時好好部署，支援 5G 網絡的 iPhone 何時推出感到憂慮。早前華為創辦人任正非在接受訪問時表示，願意為 Apple 提供 5G Modem 晶片，引發了不少揣測。<br />\n<br />\n昨日舉行的 Huawei Analyst Summit 2019，有傳媒就在活動的答問環節，向華為問到是否會為下一代 iPhone 供應 5G 晶片。結果得到的結果和集團創辦人任正非於訪問中的答案相反，發言人表示華為的晶片策略並沒有改變，亦沒有就 5G Modem 與 Apple 有任何接觸。有留意華為動態的網友可能都知道，華為的晶片一向都不會供應予其他廠商，當日任正非訪問時的答案可能只是為了爭取曝光和博宣傳，亦有可能是外界對他的答案有所誤解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/212791/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4546%2F212791%2F1%2F&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=d40478b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/212791/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n見apple同鳩通和解就話自己無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可搵一次係支那人唔係第一時間衝出嚟柒㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fc9a71b94e219520559e1473fb52225e4d5c75","tid":1111833,"uid":36551,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"睇下班屎為打手仲好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一星期前打晒丁話蘋果用支那晶片呀，話咩反支人士唔可以再揀iPhone乜乜柒柒推足幾個Post<br />\n而家話同高通和解就笠晒水扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f4a8bba940c8da5df87ed630c78fe1839e123e","tid":1111833,"uid":37808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"似華為自己放風打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4fa067cd2cea3804bbdf4dd7ba1b96ec408e44","tid":1111833,"uid":55951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e1f4a8bba940c8da5df87ed630c78fe1839e123e","tid":1111833,"uid":37808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"似華為自己放風打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:16:19.000Z","msg":"打飛機打到變柒頭，呢方面好肯定佢無乜對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e525bfb80bbd3bf73671a7be4809934da7fc9e8","tid":1111833,"uid":220721,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:22:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09b8f39f27967009c7b8d73de9a9740385edef49","tid":1111833,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T15:43:48.000Z","msg":"5毛嘅下場，何其尷尬兼悲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069986a937576a99e25667b1a1f22e6dc7f333d9","tid":1111833,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:50:28.000Z","msg":"自己響側邊叫<br />\n<br />\n無人理過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd8cdd725922d55c22395b14e6fff48486fef9f","tid":1111833,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c4fa067cd2cea3804bbdf4dd7ba1b96ec408e44","tid":1111833,"uid":55951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e1f4a8bba940c8da5df87ed630c78fe1839e123e","tid":1111833,"uid":37808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"似華為自己放風打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:16:19.000Z","msg":"打飛機打到變柒頭，呢方面好肯定佢無乜對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no